'''John Carver''' (December 15, 1923 - November 30, 2023) was an American religious cult leader from Plymouth, Massachusetts. He was devoted to the Thanksgiving holiday. 

==Early life==
Carver was born in Plymouth to wedding planner Paula Legend (1895 - 1972) and flight attendant Thomas Carver (1865 - 1938). 

